    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1 at all five operating points. UQ campaign confirmed robustness of conclusions across the uncertainty envelope. The credibility evidence package is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device hemolysis assessment. Decision consequence is High, but model influence is Medium and the full 13-factor assessment provides adequate confidence for the intended use.",
